summary: An Ordinance approving the assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2160 for the improvement of The Alley in Block Sixty-six (66), A. A. Denny's Addition, all in the City of Seattle, by paving the same with brick, under Ordinance No. 21719, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel and lot of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
